---
title: Shrimp & Scallop Cioppino with Garlic Toast & Parsley
description: This Italian-American stew was originally created in the 1800s by fishermen in San Francisco. If there were any leftovers from the day’s seafood catch, they were simmered together with tomatoes and wine to create a warming stew. Our version features shrimp and scallops in a Tuscan-style tomato broth, with garlic butter toast on the side for dipping. Cioppino is designed with sharing in mind, so reel your friends in with this savory dish that’s sure to have everyone hooked!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/shrimp-scallop-cioppino-46fd4038.jpg
